rdfs:label: EusLisp Robot Programming Language
ns:common.topic.description: EusLisp is a Lisp-based programming system. Built on the basis of object orientation, it is designed specifically for developing robotics software. The first version of it ran in 1986 on Unix-System5/Ustation-E20.
